               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-175-person1715">
                  JAMES 
                  PEARCY
               <interp inst="t18270913-175-person1715" type="surname" value="PEARCY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-175-person1715" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-175-person1715" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a <rs id="t18270913-175-viclabel993" type="occupation">warehouse-keeper</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-175-victim1714 t18270913-175-viclabel993"></join>, and live in St. John-street, Smithfield. I lost two odd shoes on the 2d of August; the officers brought them back to me, and the two prisoners. I had seen them in my shop window about an hour before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-175-person1716">
                  JAMES 
                  NEWTON
               <interp inst="t18270913-175-person1716" type="surname" value="NEWTON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-175-person1716" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-175-person1716" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I was going to work, and saw the prisoners lurking about Mr. Pearcy's shop window; I saw Clarke go into the shop and return in about half a minute, with something under his coat - Gillmore then went into the shop, but came out again directly, and they went away together; I went up to them and found these two shoes (which I produce,) on Clarke.</p>
               <p>GILLMORE's Defence. As I was going along I met this lad, he saw these two shoes lying at the door, and took them.</p>
               <p>CLARKE's Defence. I saw these shoes near the door, and I said to Gillmore, "Shall I take these up, and give to the beadle?" he said "Yes. if you like." I took them.</p>

               <p>GILLMORE - <rs id="t18270913-175-verdict994" type="verdictDescription">
